Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:10.82,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:19.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:31.59,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:40.56,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to unleash all my magic! \NThen all of you, this human,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:42.22,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,and I will all be done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.55,0:00:47.43,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear! Disappear! Die, humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.43,0:00:49.15,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this ki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.58,0:00:54.86,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, Magna, and Vanessa fought Luck, \Nwho had reincarnated as an elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:58.72,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Humans... I will make you pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:01:01.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what the \Nheck you're talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:04.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but if we humans really \Nare at fault, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:06.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:12.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But for us... Luck is our precious friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:15.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So please... Don't take him from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:17.09,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:19.67,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Give him back to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:22.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm pretty sure all those \Npeople who are important to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:25.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't want you to be like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:32.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:34.42,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Their feelings for Luck
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:38.99,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and Luck's feelings for the \NBlack Bulls connected, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:43.41,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:45.10,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.86,0:01:53.21,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,still one of the Black Bulls, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:01:59.53,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you are, you dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:45.68,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Path of Revenge, Path of Atonement
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:53.51,top,All,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:54.51,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, Magna, Vanessa, and Luck
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:59.17,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,reunited with the other Black Bulls: \NGordon, Grey, Henry, and Charmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.63,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Aboard the Raging Black Bull,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:03.63,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,they raced full speed ahead \Nfor the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.22,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I sense them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:09.27,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,There are three elves in the town up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:12.98,sign_6730_49_Captain_of_the_A,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}The Greatest City in the Common Realm\N{\fs30}Hecairo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:18.23,sign_16031_175_The_Eye_of_the_M,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Member of the Blue Rose Knights\N{\fs30}Risakka Ondell
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.23,top,Risakka,0000,0000,0000,,That was pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:20.52,top,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,A shame, considering how \Nglorious this town is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:22.74,sign_16031_175_The_Eye_of_the_M,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Vice Captain of the Purple Orcas\N{\fs30} Xerx Lügner
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:22.74,top,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,But even that is a mere \Nshadow of what it once was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:25.24,sign_16031_175_The_Eye_of_the_M,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Member of the Coral Peacocks\N{\fs30}Protobe Collina
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:25.24,top,Protobe,0000,0000,0000,,They're just about finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:31.45,main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:35.21,main,Knight 1,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's no use... They're too powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.81,main,Knight 2,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Xerx...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:42.14,main,Knight 2,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the Saint of Pure Ice attacking \Nthe people he's supposed to protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:44.91,main,Knight 3,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Knights doing something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:47.55,main,Knight 3,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Clover Kingdom finally finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:52.50,main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Sol, I'm sorry... I couldn't \Nprotect everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:57.86,main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't give up until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.59,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to purify everything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:03.06,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Including you filthy humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:04.31,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:06.87,main,Risakka,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:08.91,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Something's charging this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:13.45,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? An enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:17.30,main,Protobe,0000,0000,0000,,The humans can resist all they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:19.46,main,Protobe,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it may be, it shall not pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:22.43,main,Protobe,0000,0000,0000,,Stone Magic: Ground Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:42.15,top,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Re...combi...nation... Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:45.44,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Recombination Magic: \NRaging Black Bull ~ Combat Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.37,main,Risakka,0000,0000,0000,,A giant...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:50.91,main,Protobe,0000,0000,0000,,...bull?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.16,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Rescue!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.79,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:04.13,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Transformation Magic: Magic Conversion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:06.13,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Ice to Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:08.13,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Stone to Sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.07,main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:11.91,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:13.39,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:16.39,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry and get to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:19.73,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That robe... Is she a Black Bull?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.41,main,Risakka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get a big head, you humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:32.70,main,Protobe,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy that piece \Nof garbage in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.66,main,Risakka,0000,0000,0000,,Water Magic: Surging Waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:38.77,main,Protobe,0000,0000,0000,,Stone Magic: Rising Ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:42.25,main,Risakka,0000,0000,0000,,It won't connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:44.50,main,Protobe,0000,0000,0000,,Our attacks are being diverted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.24,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:50.01,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Magic: Ice Slicer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.18,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:02.40,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have any magic left,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:05.27,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,the Black Bulls will remain unharmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:08.82,top,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Munchy, munchy, munchy, munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:11.55,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Here... we... go...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:17.83,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic: Gargantuan Exploding Fireball!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.71,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Magic: Thunderbolt Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:24.75,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Poison Magic: Forbidden Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:29.91,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,The destructive force of our \Nmagic is being magnified...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:33.01,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,...to take you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:43.22,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, hideout guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:44.43,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Great job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:47.75,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see just how \Npowerful my new friend is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:54.63,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,I... totally... know... everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:54.63,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Holy crap! That was so powerful! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:58.87,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,there... is... to... know... \Nabout... my... friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:58.87,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are so awesome! The coolest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:02.08,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy. I finally get \Nto fight alongside everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:03.65,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:05.88,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Henry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:09.05,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough foolishness \Nfrom you humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.43,main,Risakka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} may be able to dodge this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:13.68,main,Xer,0000,0000,0000,,But this town will be blown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:16.30,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Combo Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:18.64,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Asta Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:32.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:36.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Bulls are invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:57.59,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,For as long as I could remember, I felt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:09:01.46,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,There was someone sleeping inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:05.83,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,It felt as though they were terribly hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:08.78,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,terribly angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:11.86,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,and terribly sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:18.95,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,Because I felt that I needed \Nto protect this weak being...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:22.14,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,Because I knew that this \Nwasn't just my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:26.70,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,Because I felt as though I wasn't alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:34.82,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to survive my \Npainful and lonely childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:40.85,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,Around the time I turned nine, \NI started to have the same dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:44.21,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,Of days filled with happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:48.45,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,They were your past memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.39,0:09:57.65,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,And then an ending of disloyalty... \Ndespair... and hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:03.07,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,I believed it was my duty to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:07.91,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,And then, when I was thirteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.57,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,I met Lord Julius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:13.54,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,William! Join the Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:18.55,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,He was rather strange, but he was \Nthe first person to acknowledge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:24.14,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I guess you haven't \Nreceived your grimoire yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:27.98,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll keep dropping by until \Nyou turn fifteen and get your grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:31.36,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,He was a kind and great person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:35.59,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll become a \Nmagnificent Magic Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:39.36,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,When I was sixteen, you awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.66,flashback,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:44.18,flashback,Patlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I die?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:49.46,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,Around that time, I was working \Nas a newcomer in the Gray Deer,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:52.47,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,which was led by Lord Julius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:55.60,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,Because you had received \Na grimoire as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:11:02.02,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,I confirmed the fact that we \Nwere two souls sharing one body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:07.56,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,We were eventually able to share \Nour thoughts through our souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:10.77,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,and we could even swap souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:16.11,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,You had a mission that you \Nhad to complete at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:20.45,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,And that was going to make \Nme betray the other person
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:23.45,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,who was most important to me, \Nas well as my kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:30.07,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,You, the person I had shared my life \Nand body with as if we were twins,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.13,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,or the person who stood at the top of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.74,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,the Magic Knights and showed \Nme how to live my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:40.49,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,I was conflicted over who I should choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:44.66,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,I took both sides as I hurt my comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:49.04,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I couldn't completely choose a side
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:51.14,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,and let the two of them decide the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:54.73,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.26,0:11:57.11,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,And you won.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:00.06,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Lord Julius.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:02.57,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Patry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:08.16,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,And since your wish came true,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:10.79,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,this is where we say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:13.91,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Patry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:15.86,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:25.85,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Did I fall asleep after \Nusing too much of my power?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:31.43,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,My incomplete reincarnation \Nis also now complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:35.39,main,Party,0000,0000,0000,,William has now fallen into \Na deep, endless sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:41.61,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, my one and only human friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:46.59,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,William... Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:54.21,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Now there is no longer any human I cannot kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:59.79,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Licht should be heading to the \Nroyal capital along with Raia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:01.76,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I must hurry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:07.34,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Clover Castle... The center of\N the humans' foolish bigotry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:10.18,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,It's where the royalty, \Nour most hated enemies, live,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:14.06,italics,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,and where we shall exact our revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:32.65,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In the moment of reincarnation, \Nthe fear for his life,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:34.66,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,immense hatred, and anger
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:39.25,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,made Rades's magic, which could only \Ncontrol the dead up until that point, grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:43.73,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,This was the perfection of true wraith magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:47.74,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,This evolved magic was just barely \Nable to return the souls
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:51.26,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,that were about to be sacrificed \Nfor reincarnation to their bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:57.94,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Licht!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:03.65,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you trick me, \Nuse me, and then kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:08.83,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for this! You'll pay for \Nthis if it's the last thing I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:11.07,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Right, guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.99,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Valtos!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:15.70,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Sally!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:20.50,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You got lucky. You two just barely made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:24.34,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to kill him together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:28.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:30.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All three of them have been freed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:35.02,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:40.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:44.57,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Heya, Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:49.49,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna use you guys to get my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.72,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The Eye of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:54.37,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,They attacked our base.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:15:00.35,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the ones who destroyed my \Nvegetable garden back at the base?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:03.59,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Those who waste food shall pay, la!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:04.79,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:10.53,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You guys piss me off, too, but right now,\N I want to kill that bastard Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:11.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:16.35,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,He tricked me, tricked {\i1}us{\i0}, \Nused us however he wanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:21.15,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,and then sacrificed us for his own goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.98,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to pay for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:27.19,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, if it's the last thing I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:30.22,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Licht is heading to the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:32.53,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably there by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:37.54,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,If we power up Valtos's spatial magic \Nwith Sally's Dark Magic Items,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:42.04,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be able to transport \Nthis moving base of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:44.70,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,We'd be in the royal capital in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:49.10,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You guys want to hurry to the \Nroyal capital, too, don't you? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:51.53,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Then we have the same goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:54.22,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:56.43,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Not a bad deal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:59.27,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you, I'll kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:01.60,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you, Licht!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:06.64,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the mana, it feels like all \Nthe elves are heading to the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:12.83,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't it too convenient that you \Njust suddenly showed up to ask for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:16.40,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're going to coopera—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.70,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:24.00,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:27.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We have the same goal?! \NIt's not the same at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:28.16,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:30.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're fighting to protect!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:33.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're not helping anyone \Nfor the sake of revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:35.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:41.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're the guy who attacked all those \Ninnocent people at the royal capital before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:46.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And now you want revenge? \NYou can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:49.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,"Revenge," my ass, you stupid jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:51.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,First, you need to atone for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:55.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, you're going \Nto help save the kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:58.54,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! You can't be serious, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:00.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:06.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,With that, we're in a hurry to get to \Nthe royal capital, so thanks for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:09.99,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Who died and made you the boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:12.46,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,This deal is null and void! Null and void!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:15.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away! \NYou're gonna help us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.89,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so strong, damn it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:20.05,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That's so Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:23.64,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah, Asta! You get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:28.05,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,But hey, if we're just heading to the \Nroyal capital, do we really need that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:29.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:29.98,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:34.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Luck's exactly right. I'll just \Nmake a deal with these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:35.61,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:38.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What do you think about all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:40.70,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:45.77,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to see Master Licht \Nagain and find out the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:49.46,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you for that reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:53.50,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,If Master Licht's words were nothing but lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:56.12,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,then I am nothing more than a sinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:58.97,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Seeking atonement might be good for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:02.75,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Valtos, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:06.23,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sally! You want revenge, too, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:09.62,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have my glasses, so I can't see too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:11.50,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about your glasses right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:16.97,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I was only with Master Licht because he \Nlet me do all the experiments I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:19.67,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights always get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:23.87,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I'm happy that I'm \Nalive again and can do my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:26.79,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a whole bunch of stuff when I was dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:29.14,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,so I think I'm about to have \Nsome kind of breakthrough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:32.46,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You're only alive again because of me, Sally!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:35.10,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess. Thanks, Rades.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.23,0:18:39.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to examine my body, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:43.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If you help us out and this battle ends,\N you can examine me all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:44.72,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:47.86,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Asta?! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:50.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,On one condition. \NNothing that hurts really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:51.61,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:52.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "Aw..." me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:56.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You can do all the experiments \Nand research you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:58.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,as long as you don't harm or bother anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:00.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, if you did research \Nthat'd help everyone out,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:03.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,we'd all be happy to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:05.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That'd make you happy, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:09.22,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:12.57,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,but if that'll let me do more research,\N I guess I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:13.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you should!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:16.68,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need any anesthesia \Nwhen I cut you apart, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:17.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:19.83,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious, Sally!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:22.80,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who brought you back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:24.80,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have enough time to reflect?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:28.81,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up. You're nothing but skin and bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.57,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La? La?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:38.38,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is... My magic is recovering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:40.59,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:43.32,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving! Gimme, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:45.84,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,No one can fight on an empty stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:47.08,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:53.46,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,It's so yummy! I want to dissect \Nsomething even more now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:55.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you use anesthesia, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:58.13,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You jerks...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:02.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Feel like saving the kingdom yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:06.43,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Go on... You know you're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:08.14,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:13.29,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good. My magic's recovering.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:17.50,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,And I feel more energetic. \NNothing beats eating with friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:21.46,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine why you wouldn't \Nwant to eat something so yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:24.42,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This is so good! So fricking good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:26.83,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I feel totally motivated now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:30.66,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,De...li...cious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:33.09,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:35.09,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait, you were dead up until a while ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:38.83,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason I'm able to eat \Nyummy things is because I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:40.38,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:44.89,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:47.13,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to the royal capital with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:50.45,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not gonna do whatever you want me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:52.39,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna do whatever the hell I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:55.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to ask us to take you with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:59.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad! You're gonna \Nsave the kingdom with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:00.90,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:04.79,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, eat up! There's plenty \Nmore where that came from, la!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:10.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Hurry up and eat so \Nyou can get back on your feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:13.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Recover all your magic, and let's \Nhead to the royal capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:17.26,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:16.74,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
