Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.75,0:22:51.90,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:55.93,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Rades,\NSally,\NValtos
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.39,0:22:53.49,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Rades.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.49,0:22:54.41,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Sally.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.41,0:22:55.93,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Valtos.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:22:58.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're fighting to protect!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.70,0:23:01.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're not helping anyone \Nfor the sake of revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:02.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:04.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Clover Twist!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:07.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse Clover Hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:10.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Clover Backbreaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.32,0:23:13.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Clover Hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.32,0:23:16.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Tombstone Clover Driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.32,0:23:24.14,top,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four, \Nfive, six, seven, eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:18.47,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt? Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.47,0:23:21.53,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I won't have to use anesthesia now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.53,0:23:23.01,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.01,0:23:24.14,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Piss off!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.14,0:23:24.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:27.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Clover OLAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:34.18,top,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Nine, ten, eleven, twelve, \Nthirteen, fourteen, fifteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:31.27,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I can dissect you now without \Nusing anesthesia, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.27,0:23:32.41,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Heck yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.41,0:23:34.18,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "Heck yes!" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:36.71,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,And what the hell are you even counting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:38.93,top,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Sixteen, seventeen, eighteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.56,0:23:49.69,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black... Clover{\i0}, Page... 107: \N"The Battle for Clover Castle."
